codex
The compiler now uses normalized entry paths internally, but the base bundler cache key was still using the caller’s spelling. I’m adding a small base-bundler cache-key normalization for relative/absolute Solidity paths so reads, writes, and compilation enter with the same path.
apply patch
patch: completed
/Users/williamcory/tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/base-bundler/src/resolveCacheKey.js
/Users/williamcory/tevm-monorepo/bundler-packages/base-bundler/src/resolveModuleAsync.js
